offset_bottom = 545.0
text = "welcome to level 2 of chef cat

your second dish to make is a main of pasta
the tomato sauce will spoil after 20 seconds

* you need to remember to keep the lid off when cooking the pasta during the dish making scene *

you need to collect all these ingredients:
 - pasta
 - tomato sauce
 - mushrooms

controls:
left/right movement - a/d keys or arrow keys
jump - space, w key or up arrow
sprint - shift
pick up ingredients - left mouse button (LMB)
enter the kitchen - right mouse button (RMB)

make it through the obstacles, collect the ingredients, reach the kitchen and then make the dish!"

